article.headline: Thomas scores 25 as Austin Peay defeats Georgia State 62-50
article.description: — LJ Thomas had 25 points in Austin Peay's 62-50 win over Georgia State on Tuesday.
article.linkText: Thomas scores 25 as Austin Peay defeats Georgia State 62-50
article.story: JACKSONVILLE, Fla. -- — LJ Thomas had 25 points in Austin Peay's 62-50 win over Georgia State on Tuesday. Thomas added five assists for the Governors (4-2). Tekao Carpenter scored 12 points while finishing 4 of 9 from 3-point range. The Panthers (3-3) were led by Zarigue Nutter, who recorded 17 points. Malachi Brown added 10 points and two steals for Georgia State. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
